{
  "page": "Feature quote/235",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“We had <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">one king</a>, then <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">five</a>. Now all I see are crows, squabbling over the corpse of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Harlaw\" title=\"Rodrik Harlaw\">Rodrik Harlaw</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, The Kraken's Daughter.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406183402\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 91/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 342/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 537/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.482      1 -total\n100.00%    4.482      1 Template:Ref\n 62.54%    2.803      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw